6. Multiplication Table for a Given Integer

Write a program in C to display the multiplication table for a given integer.
Test Data :
Input the number (Table to be calculated) : 15
Expected Output :
15 X 1 = 15
...
...
15 X 10 = 150

solution:

#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
  int i,n;
  scanf("%d",&n);
  for(i=1;i<=n;i++)
  {
   printf("%d X %d=%d\n",n,i,i*n);
  }
}

